<paragraph id="8BE522713610FFB0F0E5FDD9FBB4A44A" blockId="15.[136,1452,432,699]" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">
Remarks. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB5F803610FFB0F172FDD9FE63A428" author="Bologna &amp; Meloidae" box="[298,465,536,560]" pageId="15" pageNumber="81" pagination="384 - 390" refId="ref16807" refString="Bologna, M. A. 2008. Meloidae. In: Lobl, I., Smetana, A. (eds), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 5: Tenebrionoidea). Apollo Books, Stenstrup. pp. 384 - 390." type="book chapter" year="2008">Bologna (2008)</bibRefCitation>
transferred this species to the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C5A59F23610FFB0F301FDD9FC1DA428" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1817" box="[857,943,536,560]" class="Insecta" family="Meloidae" genus="Hycleus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="81" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B92EFE633610FFB0F301FDD9FC1DA428" box="[857,943,536,560]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">Hycleus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. However, according to its original description, this species should be transferred back to the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C5A59F23610FFB0F2E9FDFAFCA3A44B" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1775" box="[689,785,571,595]" class="Insecta" family="Meloidae" genus="Mylabris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="81" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B92EFE633610FFB0F2E9FDFAFCA3A44B" box="[689,785,571,595]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">Mylabris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="4C5A59F23610FFB0F3D1FDFAFBB2A44B" authorityName="Kuzin" authorityYear="1954" box="[905,1024,571,595]" class="Insecta" family="Meloidae" genus="Mylabris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="81" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Chalcabris">
<emphasis id="B92EFE633610FFB0F3D1FDFAFBB2A44B" box="[905,1024,571,595]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">Chalcabris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE522713610FFB0F0E5FD9CFDACA4A3" blockId="15.[136,1452,432,699]" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">
Additionally, we reexamined some nominated specimens (not from 
<collectingRegion id="499EEC933610FFB0F3DDFD9CFC66A46D" box="[901,980,605,629]" country="China" name="Xizang" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">Xizang</collectingRegion>
) from Prof. Tan (
<collectionCode id="ED4BBAB43610FFB0F4D0FD9CFB68A46D" box="[1160,1242,605,629]" country="China" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/crjh-4ne1" name="Institute of Zoology, Chinese Academy of Sciences" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">IZCAS</collectionCode>
), which are actually the misidentification of 
<taxonomicName id="4C5A59F23610FFB0F1D4FD41FDCFA480" authority="" authorityName="Kuzin" authorityYear="1954" box="[396,637,640,664]" class="Insecta" family="Meloidae" genus="Mylabris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="81" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Chalcabris">
<emphasis id="B92EFE633610FFB0F1D4FD41FE5EA480" box="[396,492,640,664]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">Mylabris</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B92EFE633610FFB0F1A5FD41FDC1A480" box="[509,627,640,664]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">Chalcabris</emphasis>
)
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B92EFE633610FFB0F2DDFD41FCB3A480" box="[645,769,640,664]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">splendidula</emphasis>
(Pallas, 1781). Thus, the validity of 
<taxonomicName id="4C5A59F23610FFB0F4C9FD40FAA7A480" authorityName="Tan One" authorityYear="1981" box="[1169,1301,640,664]" class="Insecta" family="Meloidae" genus="Mylabris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="81" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bistillata">
<emphasis id="B92EFE633610FFB0F4C9FD40FAA7A480" box="[1169,1301,640,664]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">M. bistillata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should be reconfirmed after reexamined the 
<typeStatus id="54E19CD33610FFB0F186FD62FDA8A4A3" box="[478,538,675,699]" pageId="15" pageNumber="81">types</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
